<%_ } _%>

## Auth Rules

<%_ if (Array.isArray(selections.modules) && selections.modules.includes('auth')) { _%>
- Auth starter module is selected and is Prisma-backed.
<%_ if (selectedOptionIds.includes('redis')) { _%>
- Auth sessions and access-token blocklisting use Redis. Do not add Prisma refresh-session or revoked-token models.
<%_ } else { _%>
- Auth sessions and access-token blocklisting use Prisma models. Do not add Redis auth session code.
<%_ } _%>
- Keep password hashing, token creation, guards, strategies, and DTOs in the generated auth module structure for the selected architecture.
<%_ } else { _%>
- Auth starter module is not selected. Do not add auth guards, JWT modules, passport strategies, user session storage, or auth DTOs unless requested.
<%_ } _%>

## Commands

