## Review Checklist

- Does the change match the selected stack?
- Did any unselected dependency, import, config, environment variable, file, or service appear?
- Are Nest providers/controllers/modules wired completely?
- Are DTO validation rules and tests updated when behavior changes?
- Are generated or external artifacts avoided unless they are part of the selected stack?
